33 SUMMARY
3344 This amendment, which is the minority report of the committee, replaces the bill with
3355 a resolve establishing the Working Group on the Reorganization of the Maine Turnpike
3366 Authority to create a plan for the integration of the Maine Turnpike Authority within the
3377 Department of Transportation. The working group must submit a report that includes its
3388 plan and suggested legislation to the Office of the Governor, the Joint Standing Committee
3399 on Transportation and the Joint Standing Committee on Appropriations and Financial
4400 Affairs no later than January 31, 2026. The Joint Standing Committee on Transportation
